game.name: Frozen Party Prep
game.description:
The most awaited prom party is going to take place tonight. These two lovely frozen sisters seek for the gorgeous looks. They find a lovely boutique near their home and have made out a plan to shop for their desired outfits. Would you help them out to enjoy a hassle-free shopping experience? Join Frozen Party Prep game and be prepared to collect the dresses that they have thought of! After making the purchase of their desired products, you also have to help them get ready for the ball. 
Firstly, go with them and shop for the fashionable dresses combine them with a pair of matching shoes and handbags in this brand new dressing game. Once their dressing part is done, make sure to give her the needful makeover. Common, ladies! Here you will enjoy both activities shopping and dressing in a single free online game. Both Elsa and Anna rely on your fashion and shopping abilities a lot, so do not let them feel down by making any wrong decision. 
Arendelle is already waiting for the frozen sisters at her home. All these girls have planned to have fun together. Now it will be in your hands how fast you dress up the frozen sisters to allow them attend the party in this html5 princess dress up game. The boutique you visit features all the trendy dresses and accessories, so you only have to guide them to make a final purchase and then create fabulous design.
